   |                                                                    |
   |   Pause        No Pause     - <Pause after Table of Roll values>   |
   |                                                                    |
   +--------------------------------------------------------------------+

The Pause after Table option is used in the Full Ride and Roll option to
pause after the Tabular display of roll values before the screen is
cleared to show the next graphics.  This allows you to study the screen
or to do a PrintScreen.

NOTE: The other pause option stopped the program after the graphics
      display.  This option stops the program after the tabular
      display.
